 ues\, traditions\, and expectations. During these meetings\, new members 
 build connections with one another\, develop leadership and personal grow
 th skills\, and gain a deeper understanding of what it means to be a life
 long member of the organization. NME meetings create a supportive environ
 ment where new members can ask questions\, reflect on their experiences\,
  and prepare for initiation while strengthening their sense of belonging 
 within the chapter.\n\n\n \n \n\n\nHosted by: Sigma Sigma Sigma\n\nAdditi
