DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJoin us for Manhood Monday as we focus on prof
 essional growth and career readiness. This session will cover personal br
 anding\, workplace etiquette\, networking strategies\, goal setting\, and
  career preparation. We will also have an open Talking Circle\, creating 
 a safe space for participants to share experiences\, discuss challenges\,
  offer support\, and learn from one another. Come ready to engage\, conne
 ct\, and invest in your personal and professional development.\n\n\n\n\n 
