BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:GroupBusiness
DESCRIPTION:A New Member Education (NME) meeting is a structured gathering
  designed to help new members learn about Tri Sigma’s history\, values\, 
 traditions\, and expectations. During these meetings\, new members build 
 connections with one another\, develop leadership and personal growth ski
 lls\, and gain a deeper understanding of what it means to be a lifelong m
 ember of the organization. NME meetings create a supportive environment w
