 rticipants will learn to create custom GPTs that support authentic assess
 ments\, such as role-plays and case studies. The workshop will emphasize 
 responsible and ethical AI use\, highlighting how thoughtfully designed c
 ustom GPTs can enhance student engagement\, support high-order thinking\,
