DESCRIPTION:\nNever swam before? No problem! These lessons will give you t
 he important foundational skills in swimming and help you be more comfort
 able in the pool. Learn how to use proper breath control\, float\, and sw
 im with a kickboard. \nSkills Focus:\n\nBeing comfortable in the water\nL
 earning how to float on your back and front\nLearning how to kick off the
  wall with a kickboard\nIntroducing proper breath control in the water\nL
 earning how to tread water\nLearn alternate kicks (Froggy Kick)\nBeing co
 mfortable in the deep end \nIntroducing arms to your strokes\n\nHow do I 
 Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Montclair Sta
 te ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nWednesday: 5-6PM\nStudent Recreation Center -
  Pool \n\n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can 
 be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11933749
