CATEGORIES:Service
DESCRIPTION:Campus Invasion is a night set apart to lift up the name of Je
 sus at Montclair State University. On March 20th\, we gather not just for
  music\, but for worship—creating space for God’s presence to move freely
  among us.\nThis night is an invitation to pause from the busyness of cam
 pus life\, lay down distractions\, and come before God with open hearts. 
 We believe worship is more than a song\; it is surrender\, alignment\, an
 d response to who God is. As we worship together\, we are trusting God to
  refresh weary hearts\, restore hope\, and awaken a deeper hunger for Him
 .\nCampus Invasion is about unity—students\, friends\, and the campus com
 munity coming together to seek God\, pray\, and declare Jesus as Lord ove
 r our lives and our campus. Whether you’ve been walking with God for year
 s or you’re simply curious and searching\, this night is for you.\nCome e
 xpectant. Come ready to worship. Come as you are.Jesus will be glorified.
 \n\nHosted by: I lift Jesus\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: ht
 tps://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12257629
