 eation Center\n\nWhat to bring: Water\, Lunch\, and Boots or Sneakers\nPo
 tential Hazards: Unpredictable weather changes\, sunburn/heat exhaustion\
 , limited vision\, dehydration\, allergic reactions/poisonous plants\, in
 sect bites\, and injury by running\, including sprains\, lacerations\, ab
 rasions and fractures.\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Info
 rmation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12
 209673
