CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Spring Strength Shadow! Welcome back to our annual Bench Press
  & Squat Competition. Come and test power and show your gains. Each event
  will feature 5 reps max. Whether you're chasing PRs or just want to flex
  for fun\, this event is for you! Bring your friends and your lifting str
 aps\, and see who can lift their way to the top prize!\nHow do I Sign-up?
 \n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Montclair State ID\n\
 nWhen and Where?\n\nData: March 30th\nTime: 3pm - 6pm\nStudent Recreation
  Center\, Plae Room\n\nHow are results scored\n\nMaximum 5 repetitions \n
 1 attempt per lift after a warm up set\nScoring calculation: Weight lifte
 d x repetitions divided by body weight \nFinal score will be a total of b
 oth lifts combined \n\nPrizes: \n\nWill be given to the top 3 winners \nT
 ier 1:Beat Headphone\, Fitness Watch\, Air Fryer $100-$200\nTier 2: Massa
 ge Gun\, Meal Prep Kit\, Pilates Kit $50-$100\nTier 3: Foam Roller Set\, 
 Liquid IV\, Owala Water Bottle $20-$50\n\nFree T-shirts - limited supply 
 so show up early to claim one!\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditio
 nal Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/
 event/11933620
DTEND:20260330T220000Z
DTSTAMP:20260302T043536Z
DTSTART:20260330T190000Z
LOCATION:Student Recreation Center - Plae Room
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
