 hat highlight sisterhood\, wellness\, and campus unity. Swing Week serves
  as a space for students to learn about Swing in a relaxed\, inclusive wa
 y while participating in fun\, low-pressure events that encourage convers
 ation\, movement\, and school spirit.\n\nHosted by: Bloomfield Swing Phi 
 Swing Social Fellowship\, Inc.\n\nAdditional Information can be found at:
